{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "背理分光", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "EG-10", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "浸透", "storyInfo": "善人による施しは、いずれ大地の隅々にまで届くだろう。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g8_farnorthtundra_aurora", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "ハァ……ハァ……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "痛い……石が肉の中に広がっていく音が……聞こえてくるみたいだ。なんでまだ死んでないんだ？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "力が出ないし、両手両足は言うことを聞かない……走れ！　東へ走るんだ！", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "南へ行っても北へ行っても死ぬだけだ。西は……クライニ・セーヴェルがこの有様なら、西部の採掘場も無事なはずがない。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "しかも、クライニ・セーヴェルから逃げ出せたとして……どこへ行けばこの苦痛から逃れられる？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>ウルサス クライニ・セーヴェル境界 荒野</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_heavy", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うっ……", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "もう……走れ……ない……", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここ、までか……", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbodyfall"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-60", "duration": 0.7, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 2.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "感染者坑夫"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あそこに誰かいるようだが？", "name": "遠くから聞こえる声"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "様子を見てこよう――", "name": "遠くから聞こえる声"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……いえ、私が行きましょう……", "name": "遠くから聞こえる声"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あれは苦難に見舞われた人であるように感じられます。", "name": "遠くから聞こえる声"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "脱力、脱水、長時間の絶食……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたも感染者ですね。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ゲホッ、ゲホゲホッ！", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同胞、彼も同胞だ！", "name": "熱に浮かされた声"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どうか救ってあげてくれ。我々全員を救ってくれたのと同じように――", "name": "熱に浮かされた声"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再びあなたの奇跡を起こしてくれ！", "name": "熱に浮かされた声"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇跡などではありませんよ……はぁ。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鉱石病は、彼がここまで苦しんでいる主因ではありません。私は病による痛みを和らげることはできても、飢えを満たしたり、綺麗な水を与え、安全な場所で眠りに就かせてあげることはできません。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私は奇跡など起こせませんし、全能でもありません。ただ……信じているだけです。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#4$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたのそういう謙虚な姿勢は、みんなわかっていますとも。", "name": "敬虔な声"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……あの、私の声が聞こえますか？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今から、あなたの手を取ります……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「信じなさい、我らの命を信じて。」", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「我らの身体と思考を、心臓が刻む一拍一拍を、肺葉が生み出す呼吸を。」", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「我らを、あらゆる力の源を信じるのです。」", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "これより、あなたは死への恐怖の中で生きる必要はなくなります。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "体内で急速生長する源石による痛みが、徐々に引いていく。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼にはまだその音が聞こえたが、もはや痛みにのたうつことはなくなった。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あ――あんたは何者だ？", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あんたが助けてくれたのか……", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ゲホッ、ゲホゲホッ、ゲホッ――", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どうやって、お礼をすればいい？", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここにいる仲間たちと同じく、私のことは「ヒアダ」とお呼びください。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇跡だ――", "name": "熱に浮かされた声"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヒアダは、また我々の同胞を救ったんだ！", "name": "熱に浮かされた声"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼女は、俺たち全員を救ってくれたんだ。まるで母親のような手つきで、さっきあんたにやったように、触れただけであらゆる痛みを消し去ってくれた！", "name": "熱に浮かされた声"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヒアダ！", "name": "熱に浮かされた声"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヒアダ。", "name": "敬虔な声"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヒアダ！", "name": "多くの人の声"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ヒアダ……ヒアダ。", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい、それが私の名です。", "name": "ヒアダ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どんな姿をしているんだ？　あんたのことも、他の話してる奴の姿も、ぼやけている……", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頭に傷がありますね。慌てて駆けてきたせいで、どこかでつまずいて、頭を打ったのでしょうか？", "name": "ヒアダ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "脳内出血のせいで視界がぼやけているのかもしれません。大丈夫です、私たちが支えますから……", "name": "ヒアダ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "これからどこへ行くつもりですか？", "name": "ヒアダ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "わからない……", "name": "感染者坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ならひとまず、私たちと共に行きましょう。", "name": "ヒアダ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたは私たちを、苦痛のない場所へ連れていってくれるんですよね？", "name": "敬虔な声"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい。皆さんが私と共に歩むことを望んでおられる限り……", "name": "ヒアダ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g9_seasurface_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私たちが信じる限り。", "name": "ヒアダ"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}